Name: ingressNetworkPolicyRulePriority
Description: Only applicable to Antrea Network Policy and Antrea Cluster Network Policy

Name: egressNetworkPolicyRulePriority
Description: Only applicable to Antrea Network Policy and Antrea Cluster Network Policy

Name: flowType
Description: The type of flow is based on the location of the source and destination Pods. Supported Types(uint8 value): FlowTypeIntraNode(1) FlowTypeInterNode(2) FlowTypeToExternal(3) and FlowTypeFromExternal(4)

Name: ingressNetworkPolicyRuleAction
Description: Supported Actions(uint8 value): NetworkPolicyRuleActionNoAction(0) NetworkPolicyRuleActionAllow(1) NetworkPolicyRuleActionDrop(2) NetworkPolicyRuleActionReject(3)

Name: egressNetworkPolicyRuleAction
Description: Supported Actions(uint8 value): NetworkPolicyRuleActionAllow(1) NetworkPolicyRuleActionDrop(2) NetworkPolicyRuleActionReject(3)
